==English==

===Etymology===
A contraction of '''android''', and in the novelization of ''[[w:Star Wars Episode IV: A New Hope|Star Wars Episode IV: A New Hope]]'' was spelled with an apostrophe (''''droid'''), a convention that has since been dropped.

===Noun===
